Quickstrike:





Quickstrike stammered at first, wanting to go with Black Arachnia 
alone, but it wasn't worth it. "Well, all right." he replied. He 
followed the two females along.

But something nagged at him ever since he got here. "Hey sugar-bot, 
what's th' big idea tryin' to send us t' Megatron's base?"
